---
title: Sheet Pan Chicken Stir-Fry with Ginger Rice
description: All the vibrant flavour of a stir-fry in a low-fuss sheet pan dinner. This one-pan wonder makes weeknight cooking both easy and delicious!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sheet-pan-chicken-stir-fry-3b4e5fbb.jpg
